               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000917-91-cd492" type="crimeDate">14th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-91-off491 t18000917-91-cd492"></join>, two opera-glasses, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18000917-91-victim897" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Arnold
               <interp inst="t18000917-91-victim897" type="surname" value="Arnold"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000917-91-victim897" type="given" value="William"></interp>
