                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-91-defend896 t18000917-91-punish496"></join>
               Whipped in the jail
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
